### Key Finding

> The PPO Full cross-asset models incur **50–54% cumulative TC drag** over the 2022–2023 test period — effectively erasing all gross gains. The pilot model (15.6% drag) still nets a positive return because its lower turnover keeps costs manageable. **Reducing turnover is the #1 lever for improving DRL performance**, ahead of architecture changes.
